Package cz.cvut.fel.constructa.model.role

Class User

java.lang.Object
cz.cvut.fel.constructa.model.role.User
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, org.springframework.security.core.userdetails.UserDetails
@Entity public class User extends Object implements org.springframework.security.core.userdetails.UserDetails
The User class represents a user in the system. It contains information about the user's role, login credentials, contact information, and the various reports and tasks associated with them.
